      "description": "$5,900 - Cheap, honest transportation priced to reflect its condition. This car runs and drives, but it\u2019s a rough-around-the-edges driver with visible wear and likely needs ongoing attention, so it\u2019s best suited for someone who wants an inexpensive project, parts car, or basic budget vehicle. If you\u2019re looking for a perfect example, this isn\u2019t it\u2014but if you want something affordable and usable with realistic expectations, it\u2019s worth a look.",
