    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Exceptional mint-condition example that shows beautifully throughout. The exterior presents extremely well, the interior is remarkably clean and well-preserved, and the overall impression is of a car that has been very well cared for. It runs and drives as it should, with only the kind of minimal age-related signs you\u2019d expect on a truly top-tier vehicle. A standout car for the buyer who wants a premium, ready-to-enjoy example.",
