    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Affordable and straightforward, this vehicle offers dependable basic transportation at a budget-friendly price. It shows its age and would best suit a value-minded buyer looking for an inexpensive daily driver, backup vehicle, or project opportunity. Priced to sell, it delivers practical utility and strong value for someone who understands the benefits of buying smart.",
