      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with potential? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a straightforward, budget-friendly option for someone who wants cheap transport, a project, or a handy spare. Priced with its condition in mind, and being sold honestly as a no-frills car that could suit the right buyer. If you\u2019re after something inexpensive and don\u2019t mind giving it a bit of TLC, this could be a great little opportunity.",
      "price": 4800.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Strong project or budget driver with solid enthusiast potential. The powertrain pulls through the rev range, the chassis feels planted, and it has the kind of straightforward mechanical layout that makes it a great candidate for someone who enjoys wrenching. Cosmetic wear and age-related flaws are present, but it remains a usable car with good bones, making it an appealing platform for restoration, daily-duty revival, or weekend tinkering. A lot of value here for the buyer who recognizes a fundamentally capable machine.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
